snippet.title: Mega Man Eternal: Release Trailer
snippet.description:
To download the game, go to the MME website download page:  http://mme.pagewizardgames.com/download.html#maintitle

The day has finally come, Mega Man Eternal has released.  This is a Mega Man fan game project developed from 2008-2014.  Happy 27th Anniversary Mega Man!

Mega Man Eternal website: http://mme.pagewizardgames.com
MME website forums:  http://mme.pagewizardgames.com/forums/
Mega Man Eternal facebook page:  https://www.facebook.com/pages/Mega-Man-Eternal/291374420090?ref=bookmarks

For best results, put it into HD for the video!

Mega Man is owned by Capcom.
